title: SE Grind
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. 24-hour coffee house with a full menu offering labeled vegan options, including wraps, burritos, sandwiches, salads, breakfast items, several vegan desserts and pastries from local vegan bakeries. Beverages include fresh pressed juice, smoothies. kombucha, organic coffee, and chai. Has non-dairy milks like hemp and hazelnut.
